	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106158438885536154">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<h1>Computing Milieu</h1><a href="http://www.acm.org/ubiquity/views/v4i25_downes.html">Public Policy, Research, and On-Line Learning</a>.&nbsp; An interesting, refreshing view of educational intervention and the determination of educational effectiveness.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106158438885536154">Friday, August 22, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
